main event: An engineer observed a bright, rapidly moving object at the Navajo Ordnance Depot in Arizona.
interesting points: The object was observed for 3 minutes,The object did not maneuver and vanished on the horizon,The observers were engineer/security personnel,The object was estimated to be 3-5 miles away from the viewers,No sound was heard during the sighting.
sighted object: a light, bright, rapidly moving object
